SUMMARY:From Cosmos DB to AI: Search\, Analytics & Intelligent Experiences
DESCRIPTION:Cloud Data Driven\n**Turn transactional data into powerful ins
 ights and intelligent experiences 🚀**\n\nDiscover how to transform tran
 sactional data from Azure Cosmos DB into actionable insights and AI-driven
  applications. This session explores how to integrate Cosmos DB with Azure
  Synapse for advanced analytics and with Azure AI Search to enable discove
 rability\, context-aware interactions\, and a user-friendly interface for 
 searching and retrieving data directly from Search.\n\nLearn how to implem
 ent Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) patterns and Agentic AI to build 
 scalable\, cloud-native solutions that maintain transactional integrity wh
 ile ensuring high searchability and enterprise-grade security.\n\n🔹 **L
 evel:** Intermediate\n\n▬▬▬▬▬ About the community ▬▬▬▬
 ▬\n📌Data Driven Community & Cloud Data-Driven user group\nThe Cloud D
 ata-Driven User Group is the official user group of the Data-Driven Commun
 ity\, hosting weekly meetings as part of our community-driven activities. 
 For a full list of upcoming events and more details about our community\, 
 visit: https://datadrivencommunity.com\n▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬
 ▬▬▬▬
