SUMMARY:JSON in the world of MSSQL
DESCRIPTION:Cloud Data Driven\nJSON (JavaScript Object Notation) is a lang
 uage in depended\, very popular\, open standard format for data exchange b
 etween applications and services.\n\nJSON support was introduced in MS SQL
  2016\, enhanced in 2022. With the new "JSON data type"\, is now the time 
 to finally complete the story and give to JSON everything he deserves?\nOn
  this session accompanied by numerous examples we should pass through the 
 usage and support of JSON in MS SQL.
