SUMMARY:SQL Supercharged: Azure\, Fabric & Copilot in Action
DESCRIPTION:Cloud Data Driven\nGet ready to explore the **next generation 
 of SQL innovation** across Azure SQL\, SQL Server\, and the brand‑new **
 SQL in Microsoft Fabric**. We’ll break down what’s changing\, why it m
 atters\, and how you can start taking advantage of these capabilities imme
 diately.\n\n🔹 **Azure SQL & SQL on Fabric** See how the newest features
 —**database mirroring\, real‑time analytics\, and intelligent performa
 nce insights**—unlock scenarios that were impossible just a year ago.\n\
 n🔹 **SQL Server: What’s Coming Next** Preview the upcoming SQL Server
  release with a focus on **performance enhancements\, security improvement
 s\, and operational efficiency** that will reshape how teams build and man
 age data systems.\n\n🔹 **Copilot for Data Professionals** Watch how Cop
 ilot transforms the way we **query\, manage\, and reason about data**\, ac
 celerating productivity and simplifying complex tasks across the SQL ecosy
 stem.\n\nIf you’re working in data engineering\, analytics\, or database
  administration\, this session will give you **practical\, future‑ready 
 insights** you can apply right away.\n\n**Register now and join us—don
 ’t miss this deep dive into the future of SQL.**
