SUMMARY:SQL Server 2025: The Future of Data Starts Here
DESCRIPTION:Cloud Data Driven\nSQL Server 2025 is more than just an upgrad
 e—it’s a leap forward. From becoming an AI-ready database to deliverin
 g modern development tools\, this release is packed with innovations that 
 redefine performance\, scalability\, and productivity.\n\nIn this session\
 , you’ll see demos and practical examples showcasing a wide range of enh
 ancements\, including:\n\nImproved JSON handling\nT‑SQL REST API integra
 tion\nExpanded T‑SQL functionality\, including fuzzy string matching and
  regular expression support\nTime‑bound Extended Events\nChange event st
 reaming for real‑time data integration\nMirroring in Microsoft Fabric\nU
 pdates to change tracking and columnstore indexes\n\nWhether you’re a de
 veloper\, DBA\, or architect\, this session will help you understand where
  SQL Server 2025 fits into your broader data platform strategy. Join us to
  explore what’s new and improved in SQL Server 2025!
